ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Take it, its hilarious, and fun

TAKE THIS CLASS! If you are an undergrad, do not be scared that it is a trad seminar, Professor Thompson is great and the workload is definitely manageable. If you want a survey of Mambo and do not want to take the large lecture course, definitely take this class!

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Gave me insight into cultural references, stigmas, and innuendos that I otherwise would have never known.
This course helped me really understand the Afro-Cuban heritage, something that I have not been able to get out of any of my undergrad classes.
